n peanuts, maybe they're having a bronchospasm or something similar.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031238,0.050928,0.068438,0.083671,0.093036,0.10237,0.10833,0.10982,0.10781,0.10754,0.087101,0.049714],"unified_progress":[0.037679,0.065649,0.080348,0.089765,0.09568,0.099696,0.10188,0.10218,0.098,0.093532,0.078146,0.057441]},{"section":28,"text":"That would fit with the breathlessness and could even cause some palpitations if the airways are constricting.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027009,0.039355,0.050829,0.061832,0.072441,0.082965,0.093963,0.10062,0.11031,0.12597,0.13441,0.1003],"unified_progress":[0.037903,0.055594,0.069743,0.079152,0.088803,0.099449,0.098869,0.10125,0.10224,0.10028,0.092311,0.074406]},{"section":29,"text":"So, considering everything, I'm leaning towards a pulmonary embolism.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.016483,0.036756,0.052275,0.064332,0.072272,0.079727,0.085916,0.090791,0.097903,0.10963,0.13942,0.15449],"unified_progress":[0.023725,0.045829,0.058067,0.069647,0.074401,0.084215,0.087572,0.096703,0.10211,0.10628,0.1185,0.13295]},{"section":30,"text":"It's a blockage in one of the arteries in the lung, and it can cause sudden breathlessness and tachycardia.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022661,0.0356,0.048527,0.062595,0.076144,0.089367,0.10243,0.10893,0.11919,0.13407,0.11955,0.080932],"unified_progress":[0.030642,0.051678,0.06827,0.080203,0.089975,0.10078,0.10192,0.10506,0.10509,0.10263,0.091052,0.072695]},{"section":31,"text":"Plus, stress from an allergic reaction might trigger such a condition.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025396,0.039233,0.052215,0.06438,0.075474,0.087402,0.09959,0.10868,0.11824,0.128,0.12125,0.080143],"unified_progress":[0.034708,0.055762,0.070048,0.080427,0.088905,0.096496,0.09922,0.1028,0.10312,0.10362,0.09254,0.072358]},{"section":32,"tex